                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860426-136-defend1355 t17860426-136-punish611"></join>
               transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
